Terrorsaur:



Terrorsaur looked down on Dark Mouse. He waved her away. "Nice thought." He 
didn't take the energon she displayed for him. With her way she spoke to 
him, he thought she must be a low ranking soldier.

He looked over her. "Is there something going on?" he asked, thinking he 
heard the word: Maximal.
